{"tid":1395070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係公務員cs既同n仔既同我入一入嚟!","createTime":"2019-08-01T15:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T04:07:28.000Z","uid":165048,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff339af55de4c1c075510eac3193c7750881a9e","tid":1395070,"uid":165048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"我係一名做中級公務員既廢中, 已經係政府做咗9年， 以往一直都慶幸自己做到政府工，我冇咩抱負或野心，只求每年跳point準時返工放工，5天工作俾我有足夠時間做自己野，已經好滿足&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n但因為逃犯條例既修訂事件，我醒覺到唔可以再因為以往對政治冷漠而唔理佢，唔理佢佢日後只會影響你既將來同一下代&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n9/6, 16/6, 30/6, 1/7, 14/7, 21/7, 28/7 我都有 出嚟支持班後生仔， 香港嘅將來 點解只係得後生嘅一代 會醒覺去爭取, 我好唔忍心佢哋 企出嚟成日畀黑警打 ，被補既更要付出佢地既前途; 而好多同我一輩既只係 不聞不問， 有時仲會 話佢哋 成班暴徒 周圍搞事&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我身邊有好多 藍絲同事 包括我嘅上司， 對於8月2日舉行嘅公務員集會， 公務員事務局 局長 同華員會 已經 不停向公務員施壓, 講明 唔准參與集會同下星期一嘅罷工，因為違反公務員嘅守則&hellip;&hellip; 我其實都 猶疑 到時仲 去唔去&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n但一諗起 被捕既45位義士，另外4位已犧牲既義士，我好感慨同憤恨-- 感慨香港已經分裂好深，更憤恨官鄉黑勾結!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 所以聽晚 嘅集會 同 下星期一嘅罷工， 我都會出嚟支持， 亦希望有更加多公務員同非公務員嘅 同事一齊参與！<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n至於真係有人會好怕 到時 秋後算帳, 我只能講 用惟有用你自己嘅方法去繼續支持啦!<br />\n<br />\n \b\b<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/heTw3eM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FheTw3eM.jpg&h=362a4065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XYGCepJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXYGCepJ.jpg&h=bb92afbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBtw, 華員會已經 唔係 代表公務員 發聲嘅公會 我决定唔會再做佢哋嘅會員㗎啦!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"fb4b6813385ff9b4cbe2f6faae3a46cc1c4e14fd","tid":1395070,"uid":126329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:39:21.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"a88e23465a85209bfcfda9490ff4bb9c8dcd3a6b","tid":1395070,"uid":41255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"649aa33d829635bad1d6aa4cbe88a602d25b86cd","tid":1395070,"uid":268059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:41:36.000Z","msg":"睇到我熱都血埋 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3163f3ae0aefe8ea688c2f6265375541c2699b8","tid":1395070,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:42:00.000Z","msg":"Go<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72a2318ed129d6e848a4de929998fefff040489","tid":1395070,"uid":263260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"加油！到時見"},{"pid":"2ddd984052e1a4e370424790da82fec332ab67eb","tid":1395070,"uid":165048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"649aa33d829635bad1d6aa4cbe88a602d25b86cd","tid":1395070,"uid":268059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:41:36.000Z","msg":"睇到我熱都血埋 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:45:01.000Z","msg":"多謝你"},{"pid":"2d4f464a6e453eca963705899bdf4308a120cf95","tid":1395070,"uid":165048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e72a2318ed129d6e848a4de929998fefff040489","tid":1395070,"uid":263260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"加油！到時見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:45:17.000Z","msg":"到時見"},{"pid":"212e3f179db3613efe9567c12babcc38df267790","tid":1395070,"uid":165048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:06:26.000Z","msg":"佢地愈係打壓，更顯得佢地好驚今晚有好多人嚟， 咁我哋更加要去集會同罷工，達成佢哋嘅心願!"},{"pid":"c77057e7973f807b3950933dbfec47323351e1fd","tid":1395070,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"條碼可以重組<br />\n求連仔幫手打格仔<img src=\"/asset